text: Edward cing gret Willem biscop & Leofwine eorl & Ælfgæt scirrefan frendlice.

& ic kiþe eow þæt ic habbe gegifan Criste & Sancte Peter into Westminstre þat land æt Scepertune mid all þæt þer to herdet & mid sace & mid socne, scotfreo & gafulfreo on hundred & on scire swa full & swa forð swa Sancte Dunstan hit gebohte & into þam minstre Wulsi abbode & þam broðeran gebocede.
